Because then you don't need to install Dist::Zilla or the author deps to
run tests.

Switch to Git::GatherDir Plugin

Otherwise with a local/ lib from carton the gathering takes too long.

Add Makefile for easier contributing

This Makefile and the CONTRIBUTING.md are modified from the versions
included with Dist::Zilla::PluginBundle::Author::GSG.  They allow folks
who just want to add a small change to more easily contribute by making
it easier to run tests and to install dependencies.
